---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy & Terms | Blue Gecko"
  description="Privacy policy, SMS terms, TCPA consent, AI disclosure, and real estate disclaimers for Blue Gecko Homes."
>
  <main>
    <section class="section hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy & Terms</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Last updated: April 2025. Questions? Email
          <a href="mailto:william@bluegecko.homes">william@bluegecko.homes</a>
          or call <a href="tel:+13213416650">321.341.6650</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section content-section">
      <div class="container content-grid">

        <nav class="toc" aria-label="Page sections">
          <p class="toc-label">On this page</p>
          <ol>
            <li><a href="#information-collected">Information We Collect</a></li>
            <li><a href="#how-we-use">How We Use It</a></li>
            <li><a href="#sms-terms">SMS Terms</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tcpa">TCPA Consent</a></li>
            <li><a href="#ai-disclosure">AI Use Disclosure</a></li>
            <li><a href="#real-estate">Real Estate Disclaimers</a></li>
            <li><a href="#brokerage">Brokerage Information</a></li>
            <li><a href="#third-party">Third-Party Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#your-rights">Your Rights</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
          </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="prose">

          <h2 id="information-collected">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you use this website, submit a contact form, or interact with our chatbot (Stella), we may collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, phone number</li>
            <li><strong>Property preferences</strong> — search criteria, saved searches, listing activity</li>
            <li><strong>Device and usage data</strong> — IP address, browser type, pages visited, session duration (via analytics)</li>
            <li><strong>Communications</strong> — messages you send through forms or the Stella chat widget</li>
            <li><strong>SMS consent records</strong> — your opt-in status and timestamp, stored per applicable carrier and TCPA requirements</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We collect only what we need. We do not collect sensitive financial, health, or government ID information through this site.</p>

          <h2 id="how-we-use">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>Information you provide is used to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to your real estate inquiries and connect you with the right agent</li>
            <li>Send you property information, market updates, and relevant listings</li>
            <li>Follow up via phone, email, or text (subject to your consent)</li>
            <li>Improve site functionality and the Stella chatbot experience</li>
            <li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>We do not sell your personal information.</strong> Data may be shared with trusted service providers (see <a href="#third-party">Third-Party Services</a>) solely to operate our business. It is not shared with third parties for their marketing or promotional purposes.</p>

          <h2 id="sms-terms">3. SMS Terms</h2>
          <p>By providing your mobile number and consenting to SMS communications, you agree to receive text messages from Blue Gecko / Coldwell Banker Realty at the number provided. Messages may include property updates, appointment reminders, market information, and follow-up communications.</p>
          <ol>
            <li>We use SMS to confirm appointments, send reminders, and notify clients of schedule updates or important changes.</li>
            <li>You can cancel the SMS service at any time. Just text "STOP". After you send the SMS message "STOP" to us, we will send you an SMS message to confirm that you have been unsubscribed. After this, you will no longer receive SMS messages from us. If you want to join again, just sign up as you did the first time and we will start sending SMS messages to you again.</li>
            <li>If you are experiencing issues with the messaging program, you can reply with the keyword "HELP" for more assistance, or you can get help directly at <a href="mailto:lucky.whipple@cbrealty.com">lucky.whipple@cbrealty.com</a>.</li>
            <li>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</li>
            <li>Message and data rates may apply for any messages sent to you from us and to us from you. Message frequency may vary. If you have questions about your text plan or data plan, contact your wireless provider.</li>
            <li>If you have any questions regarding privacy, please read our privacy policy: <a href="https://bluegecko.homes/privacy">https://bluegecko.homes/privacy</a></li>
          </ol>
          <p>Consent to SMS is not a condition of purchasing or selling real estate.</p>

          <h2 id="tcpa">4. TCPA Consent</h2>
          <p>By submitting a contact form or interacting with the Stella chatbot and providing your phone number, you expressly consent — under the Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA) — to be contacted by William and Jennifer Whipple / Blue Gecko / Coldwell Banker Realty by:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Phone calls (including pre-recorded or artificial voice messages)</li>
            <li>Automated text messages</li>
            <li>AI-assisted messages</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This consent applies even if your number is on a Do Not Call registry. <strong>Consent is not a condition of any purchase or service.</strong> You may revoke consent at any time by replying STOP to any text message, emailing <a href="mailto:william@bluegecko.homes">william@bluegecko.homes</a>, or calling 321.341.6650.</p>

          <h2 id="ai-disclosure">5. AI Use Disclosure — Florida § 501.174</h2>
          <p>In accordance with Florida Statute § 501.174 and as a matter of transparency, we disclose that Blue Gecko uses artificial intelligence tools in the course of our real estate business, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Stella</strong> — an AI-powered chatbot on this website that assists visitors with property searches, general real estate questions, and lead capture. Stella is powered by Anthropic's Claude models.</li>
            <li><strong>Vera and Hawke</strong> — internal AI assistant tools used by William and Jennifer Whipple to draft communications, organize information, and improve response times. These tools are not client-facing.</li>
            <li><strong>Automated follow-up</strong> — AI may assist in drafting initial follow-up messages. Any substantive advice is reviewed and delivered by a licensed agent.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>AI-generated content may contain errors. Property details including pricing, availability, and timelines should always be verified with a licensed agent. For any decision of consequence, a real person — William or Lucky — is always available and will always confirm the details with you directly.</p>

          <h2 id="real-estate">6. Real Estate Disclaimers</h2>
          <p>All information provided on this website is for informational purposes only and is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Users are encouraged to independently verify all property information, including but not limited to square footage, lot size, HOA status, school districts, and tax records.</p>
          <p>Blue Gecko, Coldwell Banker Realty, and their associates are not liable for errors, omissions, or changes in property information. Listing data is provided by the Space Coast MLS and is subject to change without notice.</p>
          <p><strong>Fair Housing:</strong> We fully support the principles of the Fair Housing Act and the Equal Opportunity Act. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion, sex, disability, familial status, national origin, sexual orientation, gender identity, or any other class protected under applicable federal, state, or local law. All real estate advertising on this site is subject to Fair Housing laws.</p>
          <p><strong>Accessibility:</strong> We are committed to ensuring this website is accessible to all users. If you experience difficulty accessing any part of this site, please contact us at 321.341.6650 and we will make reasonable efforts to assist you.</p>

          <h2 id="brokerage">7. Brokerage Information</h2>
          <div class="brokerage-card">
            <p><strong>Blue Gecko</strong>, a team of Coldwell Banker Realty</p>
            <p>William Whipple — FL Real Estate License #3535381</p>
            <p>Jennifer (Lucky) Whipple — FL Real Estate License #3535380</p>
            <p>Palm Bay · Melbourne · Sebastian · Space Coast, FL</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+13213416650">321.341.6650</a></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:william@bluegecko.homes">william@bluegecko.homes</a></p>
          </div>
          <p class="fine">© Coldwell Banker Real Estate LLC. All Rights Reserved. Coldwell Banker and the Coldwell Banker logo are trademarks of Coldwell Banker Real Estate LLC. The Coldwell Banker® System is comprised of company owned offices which are owned by a subsidiary of Anywhere Advisors LLC and franchised offices which are independently owned and operated. The Coldwell Banker System fully supports the principles of the Fair Housing Act and the Equal Opportunity Act.</p>

          <h2 id="third-party">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>This website and our business operations use the following third-party services. Each has its own privacy policy governing how they handle data.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Follow Up Boss (FUB)</strong> — Our CRM. Lead information submitted through this site is stored in Follow Up Boss and assigned to a licensed agent for follow-up. <a href="https://www.followupboss.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FUB Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Meta (Facebook / Instagram)</strong> — We may run advertising campaigns on Meta platforms. Meta's pixel or conversion API may be active on this site. <a href="https://www.facebook.com/privacy/policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Meta Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — Provides DNS, CDN, and tunnel services for this website. Cloudflare may log request metadata for security and performance purposes. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use this site. Analytics data is aggregated and anonymized. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>MoxiWorks / IDX</strong> — Property search is powered by MoxiWorks and feeds from the Space Coast MLS. Search activity may be logged to improve relevance. <a href="https://moxiworks.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MoxiWorks Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>PANTHEON / Stella AI</strong> — Our internally developed AI assistant system (PANTHEON) powers the Stella chatbot on this website. Conversation data may be retained to improve response quality and is not shared with third parties.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 id="your-rights">9. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Request access to information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
            <li>Withdraw SMS or TCPA consent (see <a href="#tcpa">Section 4</a>)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us using the information below. We will respond within a reasonable time and in compliance with applicable law.</p>

          <h2 id="contact">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>For privacy questions, data requests, or to opt out of any communications:</p>
          <div class="brokerage-card">
            <p><strong>Blue Gecko / Coldwell Banker Realty</strong></p>
            <p>Attn: William Whipple</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+13213416650">321.341.6650</a></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:william@bluegecko.homes">william@bluegecko.homes</a></p>
          </div>

        </div><!-- /.prose -->
      </div><!-- /.content-grid -->
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Table of contents */
  .toc {
    position: sticky;
    top: 120px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .toc-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .toc ol {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .toc a {
    color: var(--text-soft);
    border-bottom: none !important;
    transition: color 150ms ease;
  }

  .toc a:hover {
    color: var(--brand);
  }

  /* Prose */
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .prose h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
    border-top: none;
  }

  .prose p,
  .prose ul,
  .prose li {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .prose ul,
  .prose ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .brokerage-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .brokerage-card p {
    margin: 0.2rem 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .fine {
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    color: var(--text-soft) !important;
    line-height: 1.6 !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .toc {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
